1. *Napadač* je uspešno savladao golmana i postigao gol. (Attacker successfully defeated the goalkeeper and scored a goal.)
2. Nadam se da nas neće *napasti* kiša tokom putovanja. (I hope it won't rain during our trip.)
3. Policija je uspela da uhvati kriminalca koji je *napao* staricu. (The police managed to catch the criminal who attacked an old lady.)
4. Kada ste poslednji put *napali* zubara? (When was the last time you visited the dentist?)
5. U poslednje vreme me *napada* umor nakon posla. (Lately, I've been feeling tired after work.)
6. Molim vas da ne *napadate* kolegu zbog greške koju je napravio. (Please don't attack your colleague for the mistake he made.)
7. Naš grad je bio *napadnut* tokom rata, ali smo se uspeli odbraniti. (Our city was attacked during the war, but we managed to defend ourselves.)
8. *Napastovanje* na radnom mestu je ozbiljan problem koji zahteva pažnju menadžmenta. (Harassment in the workplace is a serious problem that requires attention from management.)
9. Sinoć sam imao noćnu *napast* i budio sam se u znoju. (Last night I had a nightmare and woke up in sweat.)
10. Nemoj da *napadaš* dete, ono nije krivo za svoje ponašanje. (Don't attack the child, he is not responsible for his behavior.)